endpoint.request:
{
  name: string (required, max 191),
  type: 'business_unit' | 'business_service' | null (optional),
  manager_id: number | null (optional; exists:users,id),
  users: number[] (optional; each exists:users,id, distinct)
}
Mappatura type → colonne: 'business_unit' ⇒ is_business_unit=true,is_business_service=false;
'business_service' ⇒ inverse; null/assente ⇒ entrambe false.
